headline: General Mills to Webcast Fiscal 2026 Second Quarter Earnings Results on Dec. 17, 2025
summary: MINNEAPOLIS, November 19, 2025--General Mills, Inc. (NYSE: GIS) plans to report results for its fiscal 2026 second quarter on Dec. 17, 2025.
